OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with further showers,
OL,7,Fthese focused across Argyll. Clear
OL,8,Fspells developing overnight,
OL,9,Fparticularly from the Central Belt
OL,10,Fsouthwards where showers die out.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FMost enjoying a dry day with
OL,13,Fgood sunny spells and light winds,
OL,14,Fwith the Central Belt particularly
OL,15,Ffavoured and warm. However, sunshine
OL,16,Fincreasingly turning hazy into the
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
